---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ProjectCard from '../components/ProjectCard.astro';
import { projectGroups } from '../data/site';
---

<BaseLayout title="Projects | lys Open Source System">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-head page-intro">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Projects</span>
        <h1>按你想学什么来找项目，不按仓库名猜主线。</h1>
        <p>如果你只是想先学一个项目，请先从 Smart BLE 开始；如果你要完整链路，再看 Open IoT Platform。其他工具更适合作为扩展阅读和工具箱。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-grid">
      <article class="section-card focus-card">
        <h3>先上手</h3>
        <p>先从 Smart BLE 开始。它最容易体验，也最适合建立“BLE 到底怎么调”的第一感知。</p>
        <p class="focus-emphasis">先试项目，再回来看实现。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="section-card focus-card">
        <h3>再深入</h3>
        <p>当你开始关心完整链路时，再走 Open IoT Platform，把设备、配网、MQTT、服务端和 App 串起来看。</p>
        <p class="focus-emphasis">先看链路，再理解系统。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="section-card focus-card">
        <h3>最后补工具箱</h3>
        <p>RedisPilot、QueryLab、TermForge、PaperMD 这些项目更适合在你已经有主线感知后，再按需求继续补。</p>
        <p class="focus-emphasis">把工具当成延伸阅读，不要反过来淹没主线。</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    {projectGroups.map((group) => (
      <section class="section" id={group.items[0]?.id}>
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <span class="eyebrow">{group.title}</span>
            <h2>{group.title}</h2>
            {'intro' in group && <p>{group.intro}</p>}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section-grid">
          {group.items.map((item) => <ProjectCard {...item} ctaLabel="查看项目" />)}
        </div>
      </section>
    ))}
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
